OL,3,CJersey's minimum wage will rise to #13
OL,4,Cper hour
OL,6,FJersey's minimum wage is set to
OL,7,Fincrease to #13 per hour from April
OL,8,F2025.
OL,10,FIt represents around a 12% rise from
OL,11,Fcurrent threshold of #11.64 and is
OL,12,Fwell above the UK Government's
OL,13,Fpredicted National Living Wage for
OL,14,Fnext year - expected to be somewhere
OL,15,Fbetween #11.61 and #12.18.
