OL,3,CJersey's minimum wage will rise to #13
OL,4,Cper hour
OL,6,FThe change will be included in the
OL,7,Fisland's employment law and a #20
OL,8,Fmillion financial support package will
OL,9,Fbe put in place to help businesses
OL,10,Fadjust to their higher staffing costs
OL,11,Fover the next two years.
OL,13,FThis budget includes #7 million for
OL,14,Fthe visitor economy and hospitality
OL,15,Findustry, a #6 million "productivity
OL,16,Fboost", #3 million for training and
OL,17,Fmore than #2 million into the rural
OL,18,Fand marine sectors.
