OL,3,CJersey's minimum wage will rise to #13
OL,4,Cper hour
OL,6,FSustainable Economic Development
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Kirsten Morel,
OL,8,Fexplains: "The Council of Ministers
OL,9,Fhas committed to transitioning to a
OL,10,Fliving wage.
OL,12,F"To support employers through this
OL,13,Ftransition, we've designed a package
OL,14,Fto help organisations invest in
OL,15,Fthemselves and help the island move to
OL,16,Fa more productive and resilient
OL,17,Feconomy.
